Type of Feat: Special
Prerequisite: Spirit Shaman Level 1, Witch Doctor Level 1, or Jungle Halfling
Specifics: This feat allows the character to use the club, dagger, dart, hand axe, spear, quarterstaff, sling, shortbow, and throwing axe. 
Normal: A character cannot equip a weapon he is not proficient in.
Use: Spirit Shamans, Witch Doctors and Jungle Halflings start with this feat but can gain other weapon proficiencies as well.